<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("partial/header") %>

  <body class="bg-gray-200">
    <%- include("partial/nav") %>

    <div
      class="card mx-6 flex flex-col mt-16 mb-8  max-w-2xl justify-around sm:mx-auto sm:flex-row  "
    >
      <div
        class="profile-card p-4  flex-col bg-<%= colorTheme %>-700 rounded flex-1 shadow mr-2 "
      >
        <div class="profil-picture flex m-auto justify-center items-center">
          <img
            src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/52af7ea41708106abb83a4127d092cb2?s=128"
            alt=""
            class="h-32 w-32 rounded-full  border-4 shadow-lg border-<%= colorTheme %>-600"
          />
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-xl text-white text-center m-4 text-4xl">
          From <span>Florian</span>
        </h2>
        <h2
          class="text-xl shadow bg-white mx-4 rounded p-2 text-<%= colorTheme %>-700 font-extrabold text-center text-4xl font-bold"
        >
          +49 TKN
        </h2>

        <h2 class="text-xl text-white text-3xl ml-4 mt-4">MESSAGE</h2>
        <div
          class="textarea p-2 bg-white m-4 p-2 rounded text-<%= colorTheme %>-700 text-lg shadow "
        >
          <p class="p-2">
            Ah! I see that you already meet my dog, Daryl. Ho, and he already
            gives you 1 TKN ! Good boy ❤️❤️ As a welcome, here is another 49 TKN
            for you 😃 <br />
            But what exactly is Tonken?
            <span class=" font-bold"
              >Tonken is a Web App where you can create your very own Digital
              Currency!</span
            >
            Sounds incredible, right? <br />
            You can create a Digital Currency for your Online gaming team,
            rewarding members for their skills ⚔️ <br />
            or you can create it in your company and give your co-workers some
            of your Digital Currency 🤝 <br />
            or you can also create a Digital Currency to share the bill with
            friends and family 👪 <br />
            They are tons of other reasons to use Tonken. Just make it yours!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="actions flex justify-center">
      <a
        href="/home"
        class=" m-2 shadow py-2 px-8 text-2xl bg-<%= colorTheme %>-500 text-center rounded m-2 justify-center  text-white font-bold hover:bg-<%= colorTheme %>-600 lg:flex"
      >
        <i
          class="fas fa-chevron-left text-white fa-sm  self-center mr-1 hover:mr-2 "
        ></i
        >BACK</a
      >
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
